title: Shrimp Creole
ingredients: ["1/2 c. oil", "1/2 c. flour", "4 bunches green onions (chopped)", "2 c. celery, chopped", "1 Tbsp. parsley flakes", "6 pods garlic (crushed)", "2 cans tomato paste", "5 c. water (more or less)", "2 to 3 Tbsp. Worcestershire sauce", "5 lb. raw shrimp", "6 eggs, hard-boiled"]
